<H1 ALIGN="CENTER">Module mod_auth</H1>

<P>This module provides for user authentication using text files.

<P><A
HREF="module-dict.html#Status"
REL="Help"
><STRONG>Status:</STRONG></A> Base
<BR>
<A
HREF="module-dict.html#SourceFile"
